# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# dependencies
**/node_modules/
/.pnp
.pnp.*
**/.yarn/*
!**/.yarn/patches
!**/.yarn/plugins
!**/.yarn/releases
!**/.yarn/versions

# lockfiles (оставляем только корневой)
**/package-lock.json
!package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
!yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
!pnpm-lock.yaml

# testing
**/coverage/

# next.js
**/.next/
**/out/

# production
**/build/
**/dist/

# turbo (кэш сборки)
**/.turbo/
**/.cache/

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
**/logs/
**/*.log

# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
.env*
!.env.example
!.env.local.example
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# vercel
.vercel

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
**/next-env.d.tsnpx browserslist

# IDE & редакторы
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
Thumbs.db

# browserslist (не нужно игнорировать, но если есть локальные копии)
.browserslistrc.local
